------------------------------------------------
--------------------- INFO ---------------------
------------------------------------------------

JavaCC : http://javacc.java.net/
LWJGL  : http://www.lwjgl.org/
OpenGL : http://www.opengl.org/

------------------------------------------------
------------------- INSTALL --------------------
------------------------------------------------

1. Install eclipse plugin for JavaCC
------------------------------------------------
http://eclipse-javacc.sourceforge.net

2. Setup LWJGL with eclipse
------------------------------------------------
http://www.lwjgl.org/wiki/index.php?title=Settin
g_Up_LWJGL_with_Eclipse

------------------------------------------------
-------------------- USAGE ---------------------
------------------------------------------------

Save your source code into saf.fighters
in a fighters.saf file

Run!
